{"tid":1698610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(香港導演) 麥曦茵指責「香港警察」, 慘遭大陸三毛瘋狂炮轟","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T05:37:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":138,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"65767edcfdedb09f06f7605e8b5fd4edee17a7d4","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"原來今年有咁既事, 無咩香港傳媒報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.... 反而美國傳媒報導左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;:<br />\n<br />\n《花椒之味》導演麥曦茵指責「香港警察」阻礙人道救援, 違反國際法. &nbsp; &nbsp;大陸三毛乘機狂轟麥曦茵為&quot;港獨導演&quot;, 呼籲抵制《花椒之味》.<br />\n<br />\n《花椒之味》有麥曦茵導演, 亦有撐黑警藍絲鍾鎮濤, 結果《花椒之味》係香港同大陸都仆直.  不過, 《花椒之味》香港票房都高過大陸. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/can-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fcan-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=4d8de89e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/can-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888</a><br />\n<br />\nMeanwhile, local filmmakers see a cautionary tale in the case of Heiward Mak, director and writer of Media Asia September release Fagara, a story about three sisters separately raised in Hong Kong, Taiwan and China, produced by celebrated auteur Ann Hui and starring longtime Johnnie To collaborator Sammi Cheng. Mak faced intense backlash in China after posting on social media that Hong Kong police violated international humanitarian law when they blocked medical aid for injured protesters. As Fagara bowed in Hong Kong and China, her posts were used as grounds for attack on Chinese social media, where she was accused of being an &quot;agent of Hong Kong secession.&quot; She also was allegedly the victim of death threats. This apparently took its toll on Fagara&rsquo;s box office: Despite its high-profile cast and positive reviews, the film ran in China for just one week amid calls for a boycott and took in only $258,000. It also grossed a modest $1 million in Hong Kong. Mak could not be reached for comment."},{"pid":"977755b4b7449437e7a3d59b0e1dea7f45d3530b","tid":1698610,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要 Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（求手動置頂）英國戰線Twitter要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7f7f1ef9ff12e92263773787591161a69cd27ef","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"香港觀眾要多多支持麥曦茵呢類導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb7d4799e9d09691a171716c38a4a250f1e4726","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a54fce34fcb91e62b75d51c09290a7b24eba597","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\