獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們全都跪下了，中央政府會將跪的姿勢不正確的定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪下的姿勢都符合要求了，中央政府會將跪著臉上沒有笑容的定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪著笑著對時候，中央政府會將心裡沒有全然服從的定義為港獨。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"只要是香港人，你呼吸一下，行一步路，甚至只是睡覺，都是港獨！"},{"pid":"0a84f58de24893bb62a1798826ac88c17f4b81d6","tid":1698610,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d875b18ca2c2d6ef61333b875e0f7718ca0b9993","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22de07762ec7181016c685b25f18f993bbe6ffec","tid":1698610,"uid":47707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8fa8f2eb0f6d1cae1b58c181bc2f2905061714","tid":1698610,"uid":261496,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"而家落左，你可以上網搵嚟睇<br />\n花椒之味係一套好嘅電影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:22:11.000Z","msg":"落咗畫都唔想睇<br />\n個老豆係鍾鎮濤真係代入唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"呢套可以唔睇<br />\n<br />\n但以後, 麥曦茵有其他電影, 真係要多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"呢套因為個呀叔真係唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曖昧不明關係研究學會識佢"},{"pid":"b5141f2284ef20b1b53762284f2c5749e1923e45","tid":1698610,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"屌警察就係港獨<br />\n大陸新聞真係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9521a0664f908621129fe9322fcbdc49c95ff611","tid":1698610,"uid":236003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcebcfefed9cf2f4129e31d5d0f93e2b9485223a","tid":1698610,"uid":34140,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"5d8674f6cee5cfdc5c4938429b93ed95572b3b07","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"65767edcfdedb09f06f7605e8b5fd4edee17a7d4","tid":1698610,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"原來今年有咁既事, 無咩香港傳媒報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.... 反而美國傳媒報導左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;:<br />\n<br />\n《花椒之味》導演麥曦茵指責「香港警察」阻礙人道救援, 違反國際法. &nbsp; &nbsp;大陸三毛乘機狂轟麥曦茵為&quot;港獨導演&quot;, 呼籲抵制《花椒之味》.<br />\n<br />\n《花椒之味》有麥曦茵導演, 亦有撐黑警藍絲鍾鎮濤, 結果《花椒之味》係香港同大陸都仆直.  不過, 《花椒之味》香港票房都高過大陸. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/can-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fcan-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=4d8de89e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/can-hong-kong-s-film-sector-stand-up-china-1252888</a><br />\n<br />\nMeanwhile, local filmmakers see a cautionary tale in the case of Heiward Mak, director and writer of Media Asia September release Fagara, a story about three sisters separately raised in Hong Kong, Taiwan and China, produced by celebrated auteur Ann Hui and starring longtime Johnnie To collaborator Sammi Cheng. Mak faced intense backlash in China after posting on social media that Hong Kong police violated international humanitarian law when they blocked medical aid for injured protesters. As Fagara bowed in Hong Kong and China, her posts were used as grounds for attack on Chinese social media, where she was accused of being an &quot;agent of Hong Kong secession.&quot; She also was allegedly the victim of death threats. This apparently took its toll on Fagara&rsquo;s box office: Despite its high-profile cast and positive reviews, the film ran in China for just one week amid calls for a boycott and took in only $258,000. It also grossed a modest $1 million in Hong Kong. Mak could not be reached for comment."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"補